title: Rosebud Baker
itunes:title: Rosebud Baker
description:
Comedian, actress, writer Rosebud Baker and Whitney both hate small talk and become real friends by the end of this interview after discussing getting sober, narcissists, mental health, and following porn stars. Watch Rosebud’s special WHISKEY FISTS streaming on YouTube and listen to her podcast FIND YOUR BEACH, co-hosted by her husband Andy Haynes.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
